leboro and consumers and dealers will be able to supply their wants for the coming year E CROSBY CO BRATTLEBORO VT n fff THE ALLYEARROUND SOFT DRINK EEVO goes especially well with light repasts buffet lunches chafing dish dainties fish and lobster dishes chicken dinners cold meats sausages cheese sandwiches etc ALWAYS SERVE IT COLD DeWittGroceryCo Distributors I When Nature Wont Our Glasses Will jGive you natural comforta ble vision 9 t I he NO PROFITEERING optometrists BRATTLEBORO VT Th Largest Optical Establishment i in Vermont BROOKS HOUSE G E ShermUn Manager FIRE and LIFE Insurance Strong Reliable Companiei 1 Sanford A Daniels Croiby Block Brattleboro WANTED Men and Women For Hinsdale Tobacco Fields Truck leaves station at 630 every morning LOUIS I ALLEN I T 9 PASSENGER t I OU 1 S AND BAGGAGE I Louis L Allen Offlce Depot News BUnd i Phone"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2020-10-15T04:16:00.090Z", "group": ["ndnp/vtu", "university-of-vermont-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86071593/1920-09-02/ed-1/?sp=2", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vtu:batch_vtu_iceberg_ver01:data:sn86071593:00415628511:1920090201:0435/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=504&w=410", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vtu:batch_vtu_iceberg_ver01:data:sn86071593:00415628511:1920090201:0435/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1009&w=820", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/vtu/batch_vtu_iceberg_ver01/data/sn86071593/00415628511/1920090201/0435.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "brattleboro", "windham", "vermont"], "location_city": ["brattleboro"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_county": ["windham"], "location_state": ["vermont"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["sn86071593", "5", "0"